Problem Statement : List all the table under SYSTEM user on Oracle Server:

sqoop-list-tables --connect jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521/XE --username SYSTEM -P

sqoop list-tables --connect jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521/XE --username <SYSTEM> -P
